author: ebourg
msg: JNDIConfiguration.getKeys() now returns an empty iterator instead of throwing a ConfigurationRuntimeException when a NamingException occurs.
The NamingExceptions are now all logged.
Added a more explicit javadoc on the methods throwing an UnsupportedOperationException.

author: ebourg
msg: DatabaseConfiguration.isEmpty() now returns true if an SQLException occurs.
This is consistent with JNDIConfiguration.isEmpty() and the empty iterator returned by getKeys() in this case.

author: ebourg
msg: Added copy() and append() in ConfigurationUtils

author: ebourg
msg: Moved the constructors implementations from PropertiesConfiguration and XMLConfiguration to AbstractFileConfiguration.
